@siretart ping, any idea when ubuntu lts will get v3.4.7? There were quite a few cves that were patched between 3.4.4 and 3.4.7.

@what-next-github i'd recommend filing a bug on ubuntu's issue tracker as the ubuntu package update issue can't be solved here.

Closing ..

> Could you add installation instructions to your fork?

@johnthagen 
What exactly do you want to know? You can download from my fork either a built release or the daily build, unpack and run it. The folder structure of the packed release corresponds to the Linux folder structure and should be unpacked into the same folder (/usr). I can't say much more about this.
